author: jstrachan
msg: switched from Runnable to using the WhenOwnerListener interface so that the owner/leader can be notified when it becomes the leader and more importantly, when it is no longer the leader due to connection to ZK going away or a session expiring etc. For more background see: https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/ZOOKEEPER-78?focusedCommentId=12616413#action_12616413
